                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for how we can inter-operate with other technologies"",
                          ""displayTime"": 97.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""inside of our Windows Forms applications."",
                          ""displayTime"": 100.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I do also want to say a brief word"",
                          ""displayTime"": 105.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""about the term best practices."",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Although it's in the title of this course,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 109.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it can be a bit misleading."",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Best practices are, in fact, relative."",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""They're simply better ways of working than, maybe,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 116.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the typical ways Windows Forms applications"",
                          ""displayTime"": 119.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""get developed in."",
                          ""displayTime"": 121.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I want to show you how you can avoid some"",
                          ""displayTime"": 123.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the common pitfalls and problems that you might run into."",
                          ""displayTime"": 125.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And also, best practices are contextual."",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""They don't necessarily apply in every situation"",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and to every Windows Forms application that you'll create."",
                          ""displayTime"": 137.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Not every application needs to be localize-able,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 140.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for example."",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it may be overkill to apply all of the patterns"",
                          ""displayTime"": 145.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we're going to be discussing into your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 147.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So think of these as suggestions, and not rules,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 151.4617225
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and take the ones that apply to your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 154.4617225
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Introducing the Demo Application"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m1&clip=6&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let me now introduce the demo application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we're going to be working on throughout this course."",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's called My Podcasts, and it's a very simple application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 8.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that allows you to manage a list of podcasts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you're interested in and see the episodes."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And within this application you can listen to the episodes,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of course, but you can also add notes, tags, and ratings"",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to each episode of the podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So here you can see, the My Podcasts application running."",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I've already loaded it up with a few subscriptions"",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to a number of programming podcasts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that I like to listen to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we select one of these podcasts,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'll see the episodes in that podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if we select an episode,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""then we'll see some details about that episode."",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And here, we can type some notes."",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We can give it a rating."",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We can mark it as a favorite."",
                          ""displayTime"": 64.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And, we can even play it."",
                          ""displayTime"": 67.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But for now, that's just going to open a web browser"",
                          ""displayTime"": 68.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with the URL of that episode."",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we want to add a new subscription, we click add, here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 74.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And already you're seeing the first bug in this application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 79.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in that the form that it brought up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""isn't even on this screen."",
                          ""displayTime"": 84.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, let me drag it into view."",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here we can enter the feed URL for a new podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this highlights another problem with our application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 97.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's got no error handling whatsoever."",
                          ""displayTime"": 100.9421781
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, entering that invalid URL has crashed the application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.9421781
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Naming Controls"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m1&clip=7&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, let's take this opportunity to have a quick look"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""at the code for our demo application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The first thing that you'll be able to see, here,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is when the form loads, we go off and we start reading"",
                          ""displayTime"": 8.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from an XML file and that XML file has got the addresses"",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of all the podcasts we subscribed to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so, further down here,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 18.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you can see that we're actually going off to the internet"",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and downloading that podcast and then doing some pausing"",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the RSS feed that comes back."",
                          ""displayTime"": 28.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this is typical of many Windows Forms applications"",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that I see."",
                          ""displayTime"": 34.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Right in the code behind of the GUI component,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""they'll be going off and doing various bits"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of business logic, and the trouble"",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with this is it makes your code extremely difficult"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to effectively test."",
                          ""displayTime"": 45.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, we'll be looking at ways, later in this course,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we can sort this problem out."",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But for now, we're going to focus on a few other problems"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with this code."",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's go down and have a look at this event handler."",
                          ""displayTime"": 57.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here we can see that when the selected index"",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of list box two changes, then we update the contents"",
                          ""displayTime"": 64.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of various text boxes and other GUI components."",
                          ""displayTime"": 67.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But as you can see here in the code,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""all of our controls have still got their default names"",
                          ""displayTime"": 73.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the Windows Forms designer gave them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so my first best practice is an obvious one and, yet,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 79.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's one that many Windows Forms developers seem to overlook"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and that's give all of your controls meaningful names."",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You don't have to accept the default"",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the Windows Forms designer gives them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 92.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And not only the controls, but the names"",
                          ""displayTime"": 95.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the event handlers are also auto-generated,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 97.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and so it's a good idea to rename those as well."",
                          ""displayTime"": 100.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, let's rename the names of our controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 105.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and event handlers to make this application easier to read."",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I won't make you watch while I do this, as it's just a case"",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of using the refactoring tools within Visual Studio."",
                          ""displayTime"": 114.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so here you can see, I've renamed the controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 119.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the event handlers and it only took a few seconds to do,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 123.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but hopefully you can see how much more readable"",
                          ""displayTime"": 126.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the code is already."",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So do take time to do this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 131.7263559
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on your own Windows Forms projects."",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.7263559
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Using Data Binding"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m1&clip=8&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The next thing I want us to look at is the way we discover"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which podcast we've currently got selected"",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and which episode within that podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you can see here, in this line of code,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 10.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the way we do it is we see what the selected index"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the list box of podcasts is and we use that index"",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to look up into a list."",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you'll see here is the list of podcasts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that's stored separately."",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this is quite a common technique"",
                          ""displayTime"": 27.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that I see in a lot of Windows Forms applications."",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But actually, it does open you up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 32.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to some potential problems, and you can see one"",
                          ""displayTime"": 34.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of those problems here in this application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's have a look at what happens when we remove a podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here we can see, in the button click handler"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for the remove podcast button, that when we remove a podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're taking it out of the list control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But we've forgotten to take it out"",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of our separate list of podcasts."",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This means that the indexes of the items"",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in that list box are now out of sync"",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with the indexes of the corresponding podcasts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 66.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in our list of podcasts."",
                          ""displayTime"": 69.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But there's an easier way of doing this with Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 72.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's have a look at the code where we're adding something"",
                          ""displayTime"": 75.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to our list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here, we're filling up the list box of podcasts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 80.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""by simply adding the title of each podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""into the list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But the items that you add to a list box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""don't have to be strings, they can be any object."",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we could actually add the podcast object, itself,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 94.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 97.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's make that change now."",
                          ""displayTime"": 99.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now, let's run this and see what happens."",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you can see here, that now we've lost the titles"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of our podcasts and that's because Windows Forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 110.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""doesn't know what text to display to represent a podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But we can fix that quite easily"",
                          ""displayTime"": 117.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""using the display member property of the list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 119.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now let's run our application again,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we can see that now we've got the correct text again."",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The advantage of this is that now we don't need"",
                          ""displayTime"": 137.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to maintain that separate list of podcasts."",
                          ""displayTime"": 139.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's just make it a local variable,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and now we just need to update the code"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that discovers which podcast we've got selected."",
                          ""displayTime"": 152.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So instead of indexing into our list of podcasts,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 156.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can simply cast the selected item in the list box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 159.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""into a podcast, like this."",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this means, that we're always getting the podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 172.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that's actually being displayed in the list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 175.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we need to make this same fix in a few other places"",
                          ""displayTime"": 178.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the code."",
                          ""displayTime"": 181.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, I'll just do that quickly now."",
                          ""displayTime"": 182.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm making this simple change has also had the side effect"",
                          ""displayTime"": 186.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of fixing that bug we mentioned earlier."",
                          ""displayTime"": 189.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now when we remove a podcast simply by removing it"",
                          ""displayTime"": 191.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from the list, it's now completely gone,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 194.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we've not got the mismatch of what you've got selected"",
                          ""displayTime"": 197.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the GUI to what podcast you're working on."",
                          ""displayTime"": 200.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's apply this same technique to the episodes list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 204.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here, again, you can see that we're simply looping through"",
                          ""displayTime"": 209.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""all the episodes in the selected podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 212.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and adding the title of that episode"",
                          ""displayTime"": 215.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the episodes list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 217.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we can eliminate this whole thing if we make use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 220.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the list box data source property."",
                          ""displayTime"": 223.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This allows us to get rid of the loop,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 234.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and it also removes the need for us to explicitly"",
                          ""displayTime"": 237.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""clear the list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 239.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So as you can see, this simplifies the code."",
                          ""displayTime"": 243.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we do need to remember"",
                          ""displayTime"": 246.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to set the display member of this list box, as well,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 247.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but we probably wouldn't do that here,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 250.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'd do it in the designer or in the constructor"",
                          ""displayTime"": 252.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the form to tell the list box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 255.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the property that we want to display is the title,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 258.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and that does need to be set"",
                          ""displayTime"": 261.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""before you set the data source or it won't work."",
                          ""displayTime"": 263.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And making this change allows us to simplify"",
                          ""displayTime"": 267.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""this complicated line of code down here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 270.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now what we need to do is to simply cast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 273.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the selected item from the episodes list box to an episode."",
                          ""displayTime"": 276.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So now I've made those changes,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 288.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we're making use of list box data binding"",
                          ""displayTime"": 289.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""just to make it slightly easier to track"",
                          ""displayTime"": 292.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what current podcast and episode we're looking at."",
                          ""displayTime"": 294.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now Windows Forms data binding isn't as powerful"",
                          ""displayTime"": 298.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as what you'll find in WPF, but it is worthwhile making use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 301.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of what is there if it helps simplify the code"",
                          ""displayTime"": 305.1481226
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you're writing in the code behind."",
                          ""displayTime"": 308.1481226
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Setting Default Properties on Forms"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m1&clip=9&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The next problem I want to talk about"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to do with the default properties of Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let me start the application to show you what I mean."",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This form has got all the default properties."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It means it's got the default icon,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 17.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which you probably want to change"",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for a commercial application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 21.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's got a minimize and maximize button,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 23.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a close button, and a resizable border."",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you'll see that currently we haven't implemented"",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""resizing in this application which we'll be covering"",
                          ""displayTime"": 34.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the next module."",
                          ""displayTime"": 36.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And as we saw earlier, when we click the add button,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the add new podcast dialog is appearing"",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on the wrong monitor and that's"",
                          ""displayTime"": 43.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because it's got the default window location property set."",
                          ""displayTime"": 45.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If I drag it into view, you'll see"",
                          ""displayTime"": 48.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that this form is also resizable,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""has the default icon,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 54.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and even has a minimize and maximize buttons."",
                          ""displayTime"": 55.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The maximize button is probably pointless"",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on a form like this given that it's only got one text box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 60.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and an OK button."",
                          ""displayTime"": 64.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Also, you can't see it on this screenshot,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 65.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but both of these windows have got an icon"",
                          ""displayTime"": 68.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the window's taskbar."",
                          ""displayTime"": 70.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, let's go back to Visual Studio"",
                          ""displayTime"": 72.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and look at some of the default properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 74.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of a Windows form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now with many Windows Forms controls,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 81.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the default values of their properties are quite sensible."",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""With labels and text boxes and buttons,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you probably only have to customize one property,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 89.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""at most."",
                          ""displayTime"": 92.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But with Windows Forms, there are a lot of properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you may need to customize for your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We won't look at every Windows Forms property here"",
                          ""displayTime"": 100.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because that would take a long time,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 102.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but let's have a look at a few of the ones"",
                          ""displayTime"": 104.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you might want to customize"",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""whenever you're creating a new form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The first one I'll highlight here is the accept button."",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This is the button that will be triggered"",
                          ""displayTime"": 114.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""when you press the enter key."",
                          ""displayTime"": 116.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""On this form, the Add New Podcast form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it would make sense for the OK button to be selected."",
                          ""displayTime"": 120.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, let's do that now."",
                          ""displayTime"": 124.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And as you can see, Windows actually styles that button"",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""differently to show the user this is the one"",
                          ""displayTime"": 131.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that's going to be selected"",
                          ""displayTime"": 134.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""when they press the enter button."",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we'd had a cancel button on this form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 138.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we could set that down here, and that's the button"",
                          ""displayTime"": 140.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that would be triggered when you press the escape key."",
                          ""displayTime"": 142.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we look a bit further down on these properties,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 146.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can see that we can adjust the form border style."",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Currently this form is resizable,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 154.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but if we wanted it not to be resizable,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 156.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we could choose one of these fixed sized options, here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 159.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You can see here that we can set the icon for the form"",
                          ""displayTime"": 165.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you've got a custom icon for your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 167.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we can also set whether this form is localize-able"",
                          ""displayTime"": 171.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which is something we'll be looking at later in this course."",
                          ""displayTime"": 174.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""For localized applications, you'll want to make sure"",
                          ""displayTime"": 178.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you set this to true on every form you create."",
                          ""displayTime"": 180.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We've got the options here to turn off"",
                          ""displayTime"": 184.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the minimize and maximize buttons."",
                          ""displayTime"": 186.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And as we've said for this form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 189.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it doesn't really make sense that they're there."",
                          ""displayTime"": 190.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's do that now."",
                          ""displayTime"": 192.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if we look further down,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 195.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you'll see that here is the option"",
                          ""displayTime"": 197.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for whether this form shows an icon in the taskbar, or not."",
                          ""displayTime"": 198.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Usually, for the main form of your application,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 202.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you want to set this to true, but for your child windows"",
                          ""displayTime"": 205.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you probably want to set it to false."",
                          ""displayTime"": 208.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And finally, the location in which this window appeared in"",
                          ""displayTime"": 211.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""also needed to be customized."",
                          ""displayTime"": 215.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The default location was putting it on my primary monitor,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 217.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and, yet, I was running the application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 220.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on my secondary monitor."",
                          ""displayTime"": 221.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There are various options that you can choose here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 224.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Probably the easiest, in this case,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 227.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to use send to parent."",
                          ""displayTime"": 229.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This tells this form to appear in the center"",
                          ""displayTime"": 232.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of its parent window when it starts up."",
                          ""displayTime"": 235.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So it will appear right over the main My Podcast window."",
                          ""displayTime"": 238.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's run this application and see that in action."",
                          ""displayTime"": 241.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now when we click the add new podcast button,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 245.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the form appears right over its parent."",
                          ""displayTime"": 249.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And as you can see, we've got no minimize"",
                          ""displayTime"": 252.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and maximize buttons although I have still left"",
                          ""displayTime"": 254.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""this window resizable, at the moment."",
                          ""displayTime"": 256.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now, it's not possible for me to tell you exactly"",
                          ""displayTime"": 260.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which properties on each form you need to set"",
                          ""displayTime"": 263.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for your application, but I would suggest"",
                          ""displayTime"": 265.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you're making a large Windows Forms application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 268.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""creating a checklist for developers to make sure"",
                          ""displayTime"": 271.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that they've set all the right properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 274.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on each new form they create."",
                          ""displayTime"": 276.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This allows you to make sure you've got a"",
                          ""displayTime"": 278.0610893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""consistent experience right across your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 280.0610893
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Module Summary"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m1&clip=10&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's review what we've learned in this module."",
                          ""displayTime"": 2.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Yes, Windows Forms may be an old technology,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 5.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and you may even be wishing that you can get away from it,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but that doesn't mean you can't use it"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to create excellent Windows Forms applications."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""With Windows Forms, there's no reason why your applications"",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""can't be visually appealing, and, from a coding perspective,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it is possible for them to be well architected,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""maintainable, and testable."",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And in this module, we also had a look"",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""at the demo application that we're going to be working with"",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""throughout the course which is an application that helps you"",
                          ""displayTime"": 39.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to keep track of the podcasts you're subscribed to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it allowed us to introduce a few best practices"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""such as making sure that you give the controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and events, in your code behind, meaningful names"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""rather than accepting the defaults"",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the Windows Forms designer gives them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So use textBoxEpisodeName"",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""instead of text box five."",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And use OnSelectedPodcastChanged instead"",
                          ""displayTime"": 66.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of list box two underscore selection changed."",
                          ""displayTime"": 69.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We also saw how it's sometimes possible"",
                          ""displayTime"": 74.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to simplify your code behind by making use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 77.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the data binding features of Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 80.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Yes, Windows Forms data binding isn't as powerful as WPF's,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but do still make use of it when it's available."",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In the example we looked at was with a list box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of setting its data source and display member properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 94.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to allow us to data bind a list of podcasts to a list box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 98.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And although we didn't look at it, this exact same technique"",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""can be used very effectively with combo boxes as well."",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And finally, we discussed the fact"",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the default properties that your forms will have"",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""when you create them with the Forms designer"",
                          ""displayTime"": 116.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""won't always be the most appropriate for your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So, it is important that when you create a new form"",
                          ""displayTime"": 122.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you go through all the properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 125.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and you check that they're set up correctly."",
                          ""displayTime"": 127.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We looked at several examples such as the accept button,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 130.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and cancel button properties, the localize-able flag,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""whether it shows an icon in the taskbar or not,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 138.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what the start position of the form is,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 142.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and whether you've got a minimize or maximize box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 145.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And I recommended that you make a checklist"",
                          ""displayTime"": 148.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for your application that has the properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 152.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that are important for you to set"",
                          ""displayTime"": 154.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so that you can make sure that all the forms you create"",
                          ""displayTime"": 156.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""are setup appropriately and have a consistent look and feel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 159.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In our next module, we're going to be looking"",
                          ""displayTime"": 164.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""at the topics of laying out the controls on forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 166.0469893
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and how we can make our forms resizable."",
                          ""displayTime"": 169.0469893
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  ""title"": ""Resizing and Layout"",
                  ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=0&mode=live"",
                  ""clips"": [
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Module Introduction"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=0&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Hi my name's Mark Heath,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 2.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and in this module of the Pluralsight course"",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on Windows Forms best practices"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're going to be looking at the issues"",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of resizing and layout."",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We're going to begin this module"",
                          ""displayTime"": 18.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""by looking at how we can make sure"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that our forms have a really good resize experience,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""whether your resizing them larger or smaller."",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You'll remember from the demo application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we showed in the last module"",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the My Podcasts application,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that resizing wasn't implemented at all in this application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So if you resize the windows smaller,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 39.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as you can see here,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""some of the controls on the right-hand side"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""are being cut off."",
                          ""displayTime"": 44.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you can also notice"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the list of episode titles"",
                          ""displayTime"": 48.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""doesn't show the full titles,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can't see the whole string."",
                          ""displayTime"": 52.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we're going to look at how we can tackle this problem"",
                          ""displayTime"": 55.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of making sure the user can see all their data,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""no matter what size they resize the application to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we'll be updating our demo applicaton"",
                          ""displayTime"": 65.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to demonstrate some of the resizing techniques"",
                          ""displayTime"": 68.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you can make use of in Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 70.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we'll also talk more generally"",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""about the issue of layout."",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""How do you make sure that your application is laid out"",
                          ""displayTime"": 80.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in a way that's easy to use?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We've all seen applications that are cluttered"",
                          ""displayTime"": 85.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with too many controls."",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This application is called the Bulk Rename Utility,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the developers have decided"",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that they're going to put every single option"",
                          ""displayTime"": 95.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the application supports all there, on the main screen."",
                          ""displayTime"": 97.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But there are I think better ways"",
                          ""displayTime"": 102.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of laying out a user interface."",
                          ""displayTime"": 104.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we'll talk about some of the options you have"",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for decluttering your user interface,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 109.0
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and only showing the information that's most important."",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.0
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Resizing"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=1&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But before we dive into some code"",
                          ""displayTime"": 2.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""let's start by asking the question,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""does our application actually need to be resizeable"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the first place?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Can't we just pick an appropriate size for the application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that shows all the data that the user needs to see?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 14.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And in fact, some applications do just that."",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""One example would be the calculator application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 23.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that comes with Windows."",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You can't actually resize this window."",
                          ""displayTime"": 27.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Microsoft designed it to be the right size"",
                          ""displayTime"": 30.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to show all the controls it needs to show."",
                          ""displayTime"": 32.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There are some different views you can switch to,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in which case the window does change size,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 37.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but they haven't made the border resizeable."",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Or you may also remember from the last module"",
                          ""displayTime"": 43.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in our podcast application,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""there was a form you could bring up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 48.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""where you could enter the URL of a new podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you wanted to subscribe to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now that window was resizeable"",
                          ""displayTime"": 55.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but as you can see here, if you do resize it,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 57.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you just end up with a large amount of blank space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 60.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So possibly there will be some forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that don't need to be resizeable."",
                          ""displayTime"": 66.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But having said that, there are many reasons"",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""why users will want to resize your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 73.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here you can see Microsoft Word showing a document,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but the window is slightly too small."",
                          ""displayTime"": 79.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I can't see the end of the lines."",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So I'd want to resize it"",
                          ""displayTime"": 84.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to reveal the data that I can't see."",
                          ""displayTime"": 85.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Also it's sized so small"",
                          ""displayTime"": 89.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that many of the commands in the toolbar are missing."",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""By sizing this window larger"",
                          ""displayTime"": 94.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'd be able to access more of those commands easily."",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if I want to zoom in on the text in Microsoft Word,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 100.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I can do that, but again, I'm missing the starts"",
                          ""displayTime"": 104.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and ends of lines, so I'd need to also be able to resize"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the window larger."",
                          ""displayTime"": 109.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In fact, Microsoft Word has got quite a good experience"",
                          ""displayTime"": 112.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""at small window sizes."",
                          ""displayTime"": 116.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""They've got a reading view that you can switch to."",
                          ""displayTime"": 117.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this view dispenses with the toolbars,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 120.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and just shows you your data,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 123.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""making the best use of the limited space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 125.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you need to remember"",
                          ""displayTime"": 128.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that not everyone using your application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is necessarily using it full screen."",
                          ""displayTime"": 132.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""They might actually wish to free up some screen space"",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to put another application on the screen,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 138.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and your application, it just needs to take up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 141.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a small area over to one side."",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so it's really helpful if, like Microsoft Word,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 147.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""your application can just show the essentials"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""when it's sized really small."",
                          ""displayTime"": 153.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's go to our demo application now,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 156.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and see what we can do to give it a better"",
                          ""displayTime"": 158.4484778
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""resize experience."",
                          ""displayTime"": 161.4484778
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Anchoring Controls"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=2&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's just remind ourselves"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of how our demo application behaves when we resize it."",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In fact before we do that,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you can see here that the demo application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 8.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""has been modified slightly."",
                          ""displayTime"": 10.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's now got a white background"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the episode title and date"",
                          ""displayTime"": 14.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""have been styled slightly differently."",
                          ""displayTime"": 16.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But this has caused us a bit of a problem."",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's now not possible to see the whole title of an episode."",
                          ""displayTime"": 21.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It doesn't show up completely in this list box,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and it doesn't fit completely on the right-hand panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now if we resize our application,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can now see the whole title."",
                          ""displayTime"": 37.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Although, as you can see, the description"",
                          ""displayTime"": 39.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""still doesn't fit in,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we may find it even if we resize this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 43.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the full width of our monitor"",
                          ""displayTime"": 45.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're not going to be able to see the whole description."",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Also, you can see that the notes text box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the tags text box"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""aren't expanding to take advantage of the additional space"",
                          ""displayTime"": 55.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we now have."",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's have a look some of the things we can do"",
                          ""displayTime"": 60.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to improve the resize experience of this application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's start by identifying which controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 68.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we want to grow larger as we enlarge the window."",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The two list boxes need to grow vertically"",
                          ""displayTime"": 75.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as we increase the height of the control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's anchor those to the bottom"",
                          ""displayTime"": 80.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as well as to the top."",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The text box where you enter the tags"",
                          ""displayTime"": 89.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we want to grow horizontally"",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as we resize our form wider."",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's anchor that to the right."",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And the notes text box,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 102.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I want to grow in both direcitons"",
                          ""displayTime"": 104.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as we resize the form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In fact, let's move the play button down a bit,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 108.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so that we can have as much space as possible"",
                          ""displayTime"": 110.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for this notes text box,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and anchor it to all four sides."",
                          ""displayTime"": 115.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's run our application and see what change that makes."",
                          ""displayTime"": 119.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'll resize bigger."",
                          ""displayTime"": 123.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""As you can see, our list boxes have grown"",
                          ""displayTime"": 126.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and our notes area and tags text box,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 129.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but the buttons are a problem."",
                          ""displayTime"": 132.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The add and remove buttons have just stayed where they were."",
                          ""displayTime"": 134.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we need to fix that,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 137.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the play button is completely obscured"",
                          ""displayTime"": 139.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""by the notes entry area."",
                          ""displayTime"": 141.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""What we need to do with these buttons"",
                          ""displayTime"": 144.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to anchor them the bottom only"",
                          ""displayTime"": 146.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and not to the top as well."",
                          ""displayTime"": 148.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And that means they will stay the same distance"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from the bottom of our form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 152.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but be able to move further away from the top as we resize."",
                          ""displayTime"": 154.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now when we resize"",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""those buttons should move and stay in view."",
                          ""displayTime"": 164.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we've improved things a little bit,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 168.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but we've still not solved the issue"",
                          ""displayTime"": 170.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of long episode titles and descriptions."",
                          ""displayTime"": 172.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Which you can see if we pick a podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 175.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with a longer title."",
                          ""displayTime"": 176.7632667
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's try and solve that problem next."",
                          ""displayTime"": 178.7632667
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Resizing Labels"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=3&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So what we've got here on the right"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is three label controls,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""one for the title,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 5.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""one for the date time,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and one for the description."",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it's the title and the description"",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that are the problem."",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""By default, labels in Windows Forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""have the auto size properties set to true,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you can see here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this will make sure that the label is big enough"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to display all the text."",
                          ""displayTime"": 23.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But our problem of course"",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is that means the text is disappearing"",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""off the right-hand side of the screen."",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So I'm actually going to turn auto size off for the title."",
                          ""displayTime"": 32.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to resize it to the full width"",
                          ""displayTime"": 36.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we have available,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and I'm going to anchor it to the right,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so that it'll grow wider as we resize our window."",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we don't have a particular problem"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with the date time label,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 48.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but with the description label we have a similar problem."",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So I'm going to turn auto size off for that as well,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and anchor it to the right,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 57.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and I'm actually going to make"",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a little bit more vertical space,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 62.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so we can have a few lines of description."",
                          ""displayTime"": 64.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And let's make one final change,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 69.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and that's to the episode title label again."",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to turn on auto ellipsis."",
                          ""displayTime"": 73.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now let's see what effect these changes have made."",
                          ""displayTime"": 77.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So here you can see"",
                          ""displayTime"": 81.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I've selected an episode with a long title,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and you can see what the effect"",
                          ""displayTime"": 84.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the auto ellipsis is at this point."",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's got a dot, dot, dot, showing us"",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the title doesn't fit in to the available space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But as I resize the form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 94.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""more characters from the title appear."",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And one of the nice effects of using auto ellipsis"",
                          ""displayTime"": 98.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is that now when I hover over this title"",
                          ""displayTime"": 101.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a tooltip will appear showing me the full title."",
                          ""displayTime"": 104.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You'll also see that now we've got four lines of description"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the label is automatically word wrapping as we resize."",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But of course you can see four lines still isn't enough"",
                          ""displayTime"": 115.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for this podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we will be coming back to this problem later."",
                          ""displayTime"": 120.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But now I want us to turn our attention"",
                          ""displayTime"": 122.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to these two list boxes on the left."",
                          ""displayTime"": 124.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""When we resize our main form smaller"",
                          ""displayTime"": 128.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""our panel here on the right is shrinking quite nicely,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 130.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but these two list boxes on the left"",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.5795001
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""are still taking up a lot of space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.5795001
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Split Container"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=4&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So the way I want to solve this problem"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is by adding a splitter bar just here"",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""between the list box and the right-hand side."",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And there's a control in Windows Forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that makes this really easy."",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's called the split container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""What we need to do is put a split container on our form"",
                          ""displayTime"": 17.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then move these controls on the form"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""into the left and right panels of the split container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now the trouble is this turns out to be"",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""quite difficult to do in the designer."",
                          ""displayTime"": 28.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If I drag a split container on,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 30.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I now need to pick up the controls from the left,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and put them into panel one,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then I need to pick up these controls from the right,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 44.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and put them into panel two."",
                          ""displayTime"": 51.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And now I need to dock that split panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 54.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to fill the whole form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And as you can see, I've managed to completely mess up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the entire layout of my form in the process."",
                          ""displayTime"": 65.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so this brings me to a really important best practice"",
                          ""displayTime"": 69.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 73.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And that's take logical groupings of controls,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 74.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and put them into user controls."",
                          ""displayTime"": 77.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's revert those changes that I've made,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 80.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and move some of our controls off into user controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that will make setting up this split layout a lot easier."",
                          ""displayTime"": 86.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'll start by making a user control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for the controls on the right-hand side."",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And let's call it the episode view."",
                          ""displayTime"": 95.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we'll add a new user control to our project,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 99.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""give it a name,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and let's resize it a little bit bigger."",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And now we'll copy across the controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 110.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from the main form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 112.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we'll select the controls we want to move,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 115.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""cut them,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 121.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and paste them on to our user control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 123.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And unfortunately, I'm now going to need to do"",
                          ""displayTime"": 128.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a bit of resizing and moving things"",
                          ""displayTime"": 130.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to make sure all our anchoring is setup correctly"",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for this new user control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I won't make you watch me do this."",
                          ""displayTime"": 137.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And now let's make another user control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 142.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for the controls on the left-hand side."",
                          ""displayTime"": 144.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'll call it the subscription view."",
                          ""displayTime"": 147.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And again, we'll copy the controls across."",
                          ""displayTime"": 152.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And once again, even though the anchor properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on these controls have made it across,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 166.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're going to need to resize them"",
                          ""displayTime"": 168.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to make sure that they're the right distance"",
                          ""displayTime"": 170.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from the edge of the user control,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 173.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so resizing happens correctly."",
                          ""displayTime"": 174.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we're ready to go back to our main form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 180.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and use the split container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 182.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we drag one on to the control, it's automatically"",
                          ""displayTime"": 187.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""going to dock to fill all the available space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 190.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""To be able to add instances of our new user controls,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 194.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""first we need to project to compile."",
                          ""displayTime"": 197.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""As you can see, we've got loads and loads of errors."",
                          ""displayTime"": 200.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And that's because now"",
                          ""displayTime"": 204.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""all the code for the code behind in the main form"",
                          ""displayTime"": 205.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is referring to controls that aren't"",
                          ""displayTime"": 208.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on the main form any more."",
                          ""displayTime"": 210.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this is a real pain to sort out and fix,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 212.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's one of the reasons why even early in your project"",
                          ""displayTime"": 215.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you should make use of user controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 218.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to contain groups of controls that belong together."",
                          ""displayTime"": 220.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Because once you built up a large application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 224.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with loads and loads of controls all on the same form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 227.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's really hard to move them about to another place later."",
                          ""displayTime"": 230.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let me now quickly fix these compile errors,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 235.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then we'll carry on and make use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 237.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of this split container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 239.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Okay, so I've got all the code compiling now,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 242.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and I'll show you quickly how I did it,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 245.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""although I should warn you,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 247.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""this is really a bit of a hack."",
                          ""displayTime"": 248.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I simply went into those two new user controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 251.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we created,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 253.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and made all of the controls on them public"",
                          ""displayTime"": 254.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""instead of private."",
                          ""displayTime"": 257.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And I did this in the designer file."",
                          ""displayTime"": 259.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this means that the out code"",
                          ""displayTime"": 262.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the main forms code behind"",
                          ""displayTime"": 264.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""can get to all of those controls to set properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 266.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and subscribe to events on them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 269.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""As I said, it's a bit of a hack."",
                          ""displayTime"": 272.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And later in this course"",
                          ""displayTime"": 275.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're going to be looking at"",
                          ""displayTime"": 276.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""how we can get all of this logic out of the code behind"",
                          ""displayTime"": 277.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the main form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 280.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But for now, it allows us to put these two user controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 282.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""into our split container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 286.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I've put the subscriptions view on the left,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 289.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and I've put the episodes view on the right,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 292.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and on both of them I've set the dock property to fill."",
                          ""displayTime"": 294.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's run the application app"",
                          ""displayTime"": 299.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and see what the split container does."",
                          ""displayTime"": 300.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we can see if we put our mouse over this midpoint"",
                          ""displayTime"": 305.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we get this cursor that shows us we can move the splitter."",
                          ""displayTime"": 309.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so we can resize left and right."",
                          ""displayTime"": 314.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""As you can see, our right-hand panel is resizing"",
                          ""displayTime"": 317.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""much more nicely,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 320.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but our left-hand panel really is doing the wrong thing."",
                          ""displayTime"": 322.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's have a quick look at what we can do"",
                          ""displayTime"": 326.5399557
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with the left-hand subscriptions panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 328.5399557
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Table Layout Panel"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=5&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So here in this left-hand panel, the subscription view,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 2.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I want to do two things."",
                          ""displayTime"": 5.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""First of all, on each of these list boxes,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to allow them to have a horizontal scroll bar."",
                          ""displayTime"": 10.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This means that if they are sized too narrow"",
                          ""displayTime"": 14.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to show the full text of the items within them,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 17.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the user will still be able to scroll across and see them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The second thing I want to do"",
                          ""displayTime"": 24.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to make these two list boxes each be able to use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 26.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""50% of the available space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 30.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And I'm going to do that with a table layout panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""A table layout panel allows us to setup rows and columns,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 43.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we need just two columns in this example."",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""One for the list box of podcasts,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and one for the list box of episodes."",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's dock this table layout panel to the top,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 60.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we'll resize it down,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 66.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we can get rid of the second row,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 70.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which we don't need,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 72.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and each of these list boxes"",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""can now be dock to fill it's container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 79.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If we look at the definitions for the columns,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 91.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'll see that column one is set to 50%,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and column two is also set to 50%,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which is exactly what we want."",
                          ""displayTime"": 99.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's run this and see what we get."",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here you can see"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we've got the horizontal scroll bar that we wanted"",
                          ""displayTime"": 108.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""allowing us to see full episode titles."",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You can see that as we resize to the right"",
                          ""displayTime"": 115.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""then each of these list boxes takes up"",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""50% of the available space."",
                          ""displayTime"": 120.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There is one thing we haven't got quite right,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 124.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""when we resize up and down"",
                          ""displayTime"": 127.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're not adjusting the heights of the list boxes properly."",
                          ""displayTime"": 130.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And that's because we docked the table layout control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the top instead of anchoring it to all four sides."",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's fix that now."",
                          ""displayTime"": 140.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this time when we run it,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.3552891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we should get the resize behavior we want."",
                          ""displayTime"": 153.3552891
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Minimum Sizes"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=6&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And one thing that is worth pointing out at this point"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is that no matter how hard you work"",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on making your application nicely resizeable,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""usually there will be a smallest size"",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""beyond which it doesn't make any sense to resize it smaller."",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So with this application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 16.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we could move this splitter bar right across to here,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 17.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we could resize the whole application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to something ridiculous like this,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 23.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and all the controls end up in a jumbled mess."",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we can deal with this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 28.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""by setting some appropriate minimum size properties."",
                          ""displayTime"": 29.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to set two minimum sizes here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""First of all on the split container,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 36.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to say the leff-hand panel can't go narrower"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""than 180 pixels."",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And then for the overall main form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 45.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to say that that can't go smaller"",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""than 400 by 300 pixels."",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now when we run it"",
                          ""displayTime"": 54.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you'll see that we can't resize this panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""any smaller than a sensible amount"",
                          ""displayTime"": 59.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that still let's us access the add and remove buttons."",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if we try to resize the whole thing,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 65.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can still just about use the right-hand panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 67.1855891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""even at this small size."",
                          ""displayTime"": 70.1855891
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Demo - Flow Layout Panel"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=7&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So the resizing of our application has improved a lot,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but there is still one problem that's bugging me."",
                          ""displayTime"": 4.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We haven't really solve the problem"",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with the titles being too long."",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""They're being truncated with this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""dot, dot, dot, or ellipses"",
                          ""displayTime"": 13.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and also with the descriptions of each episode."",
                          ""displayTime"": 16.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here you can see, that although we're showing four lines"",
                          ""displayTime"": 19.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're still not showing the whole thing."",
                          ""displayTime"": 22.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Can we get it so that we can show the whole title"",
                          ""displayTime"": 25.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the whole description?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 28.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Well one way of doing this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 30.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to make use of the flow layout panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""What we want to do in the episode view"",
                          ""displayTime"": 37.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to take the three labels of the title,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 39.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the publication date in the description,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and to get them to take up as much space as they need"",
                          ""displayTime"": 45.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to show the whole label."",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And then, underneath that,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'll put the rest of the controls."",
                          ""displayTime"": 51.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now once again, we find ourselves wishing"",
                          ""displayTime"": 54.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we had a separate user control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 56.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We really need all of these controls at the bottom"",
                          ""displayTime"": 59.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to be in a single container."",
                          ""displayTime"": 61.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I won't extract yet another user control at this moment,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 63.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""although that probably would be a good idea."",
                          ""displayTime"": 67.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm going to take a slightly simpler approach,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 69.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and just put them all inside a panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So I'm going to select a panel,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and drag it on to my user control,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""then I'm going to select all the controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 81.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that I want to be on that panel,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""cut them on to the clipboard."",
                          ""displayTime"": 85.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And now I'm going to resize that panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to be about the same size as those controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we're previously taking up."",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And then I can paste the controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 95.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on to the panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 98.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we've done that,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 102.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can get our three labels"",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""into a flow layout panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 105.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So I'll drag a flow layout panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on to our user control,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 109.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then I'll select the title label,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and paste it in,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 114.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the date time label,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 115.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the description label."",
                          ""displayTime"": 117.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we'll dock this flow layout panel to the top."",
                          ""displayTime"": 121.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And now they're in a flow layout panel,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 126.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we can use the auto size property for our labels again."",
                          ""displayTime"": 128.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we don't need them to be anchored"",
                          ""displayTime"": 132.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""or have auto ellipsis set on."",
                          ""displayTime"": 134.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now as we make those same changes to the other labels,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 138.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you'll see that they start to get laid out"",
                          ""displayTime"": 141.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from left to right."",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we're going to need to make some changes"",
                          ""displayTime"": 145.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the properties of our flow layout panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 147.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""First of all our flow direction"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is going to be top to bottom,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 151.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we're going to tell it we don't want it to wrap."",
                          ""displayTime"": 154.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So that means don't start a second column."",
                          ""displayTime"": 157.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And finally we're going to tell it to auto size itself."",
                          ""displayTime"": 160.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And then we'll tell the bottom panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that it can use up all of the remaining space,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 165.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so we'll dock it to fill."",
                          ""displayTime"": 168.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And that's actually caused some of it to disappear"",
                          ""displayTime"": 172.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""behind the flow layout panel."",
                          ""displayTime"": 175.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we need to reorder the controls,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 177.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we can do that by using this"",
                          ""displayTime"": 179.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""bring to front button."",
                          ""displayTime"": 181.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now let's run this and see what it does."",
                          ""displayTime"": 183.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So you can see straight away"",
                          ""displayTime"": 187.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that we've got more lines available"",
                          ""displayTime"": 189.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to show the full description."",
                          ""displayTime"": 191.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's have a look at some episodes"",
                          ""displayTime"": 193.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with longer titles as well."",
                          ""displayTime"": 195.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Here, this episode with a very long title"",
                          ""displayTime"": 197.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""you can now see that we've wrapped around"",
                          ""displayTime"": 200.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to have a second line of title,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 202.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and we've got the full description."",
                          ""displayTime"": 204.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we've got a really nice resize experience."",
                          ""displayTime"": 207.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Although really we probably should take this even further,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 212.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because if the description gets too long,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 216.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's going to start pushing the other controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 218.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""off the bottom of the form."",
                          ""displayTime"": 221.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we could do one final fix"",
                          ""displayTime"": 224.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""by setting a maximum size on that description label."",
                          ""displayTime"": 226.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We don't really care how wide it gets,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 231.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so let's say the maximum width can be 10,000."",
                          ""displayTime"": 233.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But we don't want it to get too high,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 239.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so let's say can only be 150 pixels high."",
                          ""displayTime"": 241.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now when we try this,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 247.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if we resize really narrow,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 251.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'll see at some point"",
                          ""displayTime"": 253.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's going to start cutting off the description"",
                          ""displayTime"": 255.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because there's just too much of it."",
                          ""displayTime"": 257.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So in this demo I've tried to give you a broad overview"",
                          ""displayTime"": 261.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of the various techniques"",
                          ""displayTime"": 264.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that are available to you in Windows Forms"",
                          ""displayTime"": 266.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for making sure that your form resizes really nicely."",
                          ""displayTime"": 268.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In fact, there's more we could have done to this form,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 272.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but we'll leave resizing for now,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 275.8105336
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and move on to look at the topic of layout."",
                          ""displayTime"": 277.8105336
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      ""title"": ""Layouts"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m2&clip=8&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now what I mean by layout,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 1.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is how can we organize the controls in our application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in a way that allows the user to see what they need to see,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 6.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and do what they want to do."",
                          ""displayTime"": 9.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now we saw earlier in this module an example"",
                          ""displayTime"": 12.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of an overly cluttered user interface."",
                          ""displayTime"": 15.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And your application is going to have data"",
                          ""displayTime"": 18.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that the user wants to see and work with,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and commands that allow them to operate on that data."",
                          ""displayTime"": 23.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it's possible to have too much of both of them."",
                          ""displayTime"": 27.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if our application has too much data"",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""or too many commands in the user interface,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 33.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's going to be difficult to work with."",
                          ""displayTime"": 35.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So ideally what we want to do"",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to show just the essentials,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 40.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the most important data,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the most useful commands for working with that data."",
                          ""displayTime"": 44.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And when it's not obvious what we should show,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 49.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""make it really easy for the users to choose,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 51.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and navigate to the data and commands that they want to use."",
                          ""displayTime"": 54.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So we're going to look"",
                          ""displayTime"": 58.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""very quickly at four ways you can do this,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 60.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then apply one of them to our demo application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 62.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So one layout which you'll be really familiar with"",
                          ""displayTime"": 68.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you are a Windows Forms developer"",
                          ""displayTime"": 71.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because Visual Studio uses it,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 73.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is to have dockable windows."",
                          ""displayTime"": 75.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""With a dockable window layout, it allows the user to choose"",
                          ""displayTime"": 78.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what views they want to see,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""how big they want them to be,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and they can even spill over on to a second monitor."",
                          ""displayTime"": 85.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The down side of this approach though"",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is that it's quite complicated to use."",
                          ""displayTime"": 90.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And you're probably familiar with the frustration"",
                          ""displayTime"": 93.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of trying to get Visual Studio to keep a particular window"",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in the place you want it to be."",
                          ""displayTime"": 99.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now Windows Forms doesn't come"",
                          ""displayTime"": 102.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with any dockable windows support out of the box."",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But that doesn't mean you can't use them"",
                          ""displayTime"": 107.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""in Windows Forms."",
                          ""displayTime"": 109.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There are a number of third party libraries"",
                          ""displayTime"": 111.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that will allow you to create this experience,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and some of them are open source,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 116.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""like this one I've linked to here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So this is a possible option but really only applies"",
                          ""displayTime"": 120.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you've got a particularly complicated application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 124.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that needs to have many different views."",
                          ""displayTime"": 127.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The next type of layout I want to mention"",
                          ""displayTime"": 131.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is using tab controls."",
                          ""displayTime"": 133.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now in fact, Visual Studio makes use of tabs"",
                          ""displayTime"": 136.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for allowing you to navigate between all the open documents"",
                          ""displayTime"": 139.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that you have."",
                          ""displayTime"": 142.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But tab controls can also be used to allow you to switch"",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""between a limited number of views in your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 146.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let me show you an example"",
                          ""displayTime"": 150.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of an open source application that I created."",
                          ""displayTime"": 152.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's built in Windows Forms,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 155.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and although it doesn't look like a traditional tab control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 157.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""this is in fact a tab control that you're seeing."",
                          ""displayTime"": 160.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And so I'm able to switch between"",
                          ""displayTime"": 163.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the four different views in my application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 165.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Again, this is making use of an open source library"",
                          ""displayTime"": 168.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which I've provided a link to here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 171.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now in some applications"",
                          ""displayTime"": 176.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's not many different data views that you have"",
                          ""displayTime"": 177.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but many different commands that you can use"",
                          ""displayTime"": 180.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to manipulate that data,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 183.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and the applications in Microsoft Office"",
                          ""displayTime"": 185.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""are a classic example of this."",
                          ""displayTime"": 187.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And the approach that Microsoft came up with"",
                          ""displayTime"": 189.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to solve the problem of just having far too many commands"",
                          ""displayTime"": 191.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to fit into one screen is the Windows Ribbon control,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 194.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which are used in Word,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 198.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and Power Point,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 200.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as you can see here in these examples."",
                          ""displayTime"": 201.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""In fact, it's really a tabs dialogue with each tab"",
                          ""displayTime"": 204.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""having separate controls on it."",
                          ""displayTime"": 208.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Once again, this isn't something the .NET Framework"",
                          ""displayTime"": 211.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""provides for your by default."",
                          ""displayTime"": 213.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But again, you can easily find third party libraries"",
                          ""displayTime"": 215.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""including open source ones"",
                          ""displayTime"": 218.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that will let you add a Windows ribbon"",
                          ""displayTime"": 220.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to your Windows Forms application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 222.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And I've provided a link to an open source one for you here."",
                          ""displayTime"": 225.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""But the final type of layout that I want to consider,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 230.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and really by far the most popular,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 232.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is the explorer style of application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 235.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it's called that because"",
                          ""displayTime"": 238.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the Windows explorer makes use of this."",
                          ""displayTime"": 239.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""On the left-hand side we have a tree view"",
                          ""displayTime"": 242.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that allows us to select what we're going to be looking at."",
                          ""displayTime"": 245.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And on the right-hand side we have a view"",
                          ""displayTime"": 248.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that shows us what's been selected."",
                          ""displayTime"": 251.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And this explorer style view of a left-hand selection panel,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 254.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and a right-hand data view"",
                          ""displayTime"": 258.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""crops up all over the place."",
                          ""displayTime"": 259.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""For example here's it in Visual Studio"",
                          ""displayTime"": 261.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""allowing us to configure the options"",
                          ""displayTime"": 264.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""as we select different nodes in this tree view on the left."",
                          ""displayTime"": 267.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Then different options and controls will appear"",
                          ""displayTime"": 271.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for us to set on the right."",
                          ""displayTime"": 273.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And in fact, this is probably going to be"",
                          ""displayTime"": 277.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the most appropriate layout for our"",
                          ""displayTime"": 279.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""my podcasts application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 283.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""As on the left we're going to select"",
                          ""displayTime"": 285.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which podcast and episode we want to listen to,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 287.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and then on the right, we've got our controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 289.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that show us data about the selected podcast,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 292.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and allow us to rate it and make notes on it."",
                          ""displayTime"": 295.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There is several benefits to making use of an explorer style"",
                          ""displayTime"": 300.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for your application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 303.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""First starters it's a well-known paradigm,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 305.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""your users will immediately know what to do."",
                          ""displayTime"": 307.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It's easy to navigate,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 310.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's versatile."",
                          ""displayTime"": 312.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""It can be applied to many different types of application,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 313.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and it's particularly useful in line"",
                          ""displayTime"": 316.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of business applications,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 317.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""where you need to navigate and edit"",
                          ""displayTime"": 319.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""lots of different business domain objects."",
                          ""displayTime"": 321.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And it's quite simple as well,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 324.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""because you're only looking at one view of data at a time."",
                          ""displayTime"": 326.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""There are however some challenges you'll need to be aware of"",
                          ""displayTime"": 331.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you're using the explorer style of layout."",
                          ""displayTime"": 334.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""One is, is it going to take a long time to discover"",
                          ""displayTime"": 338.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what nodes need to be shown in the left-hand tree view?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 342.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If it is going to take a long time"",
                          ""displayTime"": 346.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""then you may need to consider a synchronous loading"",
                          ""displayTime"": 348.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of your tree view."",
                          ""displayTime"": 351.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You may also find you need to sync your changes"",
                          ""displayTime"": 353.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""from the right-hand panel to the left."",
                          ""displayTime"": 356.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""If you can edit somebody's name on the right-hand panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 359.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""does that mean that the left-hand panel with the tree view"",
                          ""displayTime"": 361.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""needs to be updated to reflect your changes?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 365.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Of if you can delete something on the right-hand panel"",
                          ""displayTime"": 368.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is it going to disappear"",
                          ""displayTime"": 371.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""out of the tree view panel on the left?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 372.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Another big problem you can run into"",
                          ""displayTime"": 376.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""particularly with line of business type applications"",
                          ""displayTime"": 378.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that use explorer style,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 381.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is when the user decides they want to navigate away"",
                          ""displayTime"": 383.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to a different node,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 385.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what happens if they've got some unsaved data?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 387.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Are you going to automatically save it for them,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 390.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""or ask them if they want to save it?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 393.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And if they do want it save it as they navigate away"",
                          ""displayTime"": 396.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what happens if there's a validation error,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 399.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and it wasn't able to save?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 402.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Are you going to stop them navigating away"",
                          ""displayTime"": 404.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to a new node?"",
                          ""displayTime"": 406.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So often you need to implement"",
                          ""displayTime"": 407.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the ability to cancel navigation from one node to another."",
                          ""displayTime"": 409.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So the explorer style isn't without as difficulties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 415.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""but I think in the case of our application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 418.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it's exactly what we need."",
                          ""displayTime"": 420.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So let's go and quickly update our application"",
                          ""displayTime"": 421.5518448
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to have an explorer style."",
                          ""displayTime"": 424.5518448
                        }
                      ]
