                    {
                      ""title"": ""Adding in Scrollbars"",
                      ""playerUrl"": ""//app.pluralsight.com/player?course=windows-forms-best-practices&author=mark-heath&name=windows-forms-best-practices-m6&clip=5&mode=live"",
                      ""segments"": [
                        {
                          ""text"": ""So to add scrolling support to our Wave Form Viewer class"",
                          ""displayTime"": 3.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I'm actually going to use HScrollbar to add a horizontal"",
                          ""displayTime"": 7.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""scroll bar, now you may be wondering why I'm not going"",
                          ""displayTime"": 11.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to use AutoScroll when I said that user controls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 14.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""support auto-scrolling and the reason is to get"",
                          ""displayTime"": 17.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""auto-scrolling working for a waveform control what we'd need"",
                          ""displayTime"": 20.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to do is put a panel inside our user control that"",
                          ""displayTime"": 24.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""was the full width of the waveform so for an hour's podcast"",
                          ""displayTime"": 27.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it would need to be 3,600 pixels wide."",
                          ""displayTime"": 31.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'd then paint the whole waveform onto that panel and then"",
                          ""displayTime"": 34.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we'd could just turn on AutoScroll for our user control."",
                          ""displayTime"": 38.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now in some circumstances that may be the best option"",
                          ""displayTime"": 42.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to choose but I don't think that's particularly quite from a"",
                          ""displayTime"": 44.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""performance perspective so we'll manage our own scrolling"",
                          ""displayTime"": 47.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""with a horizontal scroll bar."",
                          ""displayTime"": 50.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let me drag one onto the Control and I'm going to dock it"",
                          ""displayTime"": 53.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the bottom and now we need to make some changes"",
                          ""displayTime"": 57.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to our Wave Form Viewer."",
                          ""displayTime"": 62.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""First of all the presence of the scroll bar means that we"",
                          ""displayTime"": 65.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""don't have quite as much height available"",
                          ""displayTime"": 67.4409891
                        },
                        {
