                          ""displayTime"": 69.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's create a new property called AvailableHeight which is"",
                          ""displayTime"": 72.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the height of the control minus"",
                          ""displayTime"": 76.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the height of the scroll bar."",
                          ""displayTime"": 79.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""The height of the line will, therefore, be based"",
                          ""displayTime"": 82.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on the available height and the top calculation needs to"",
                          ""displayTime"": 83.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""take into account the available height."",
                          ""displayTime"": 88.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We also need to set up some properties"",
                          ""displayTime"": 92.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""on the horizontal scroll bar including"",
                          ""displayTime"": 94.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""what's its maximum value which will be the number"",
                          ""displayTime"": 96.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of peaks that we have so I've created a Calculate"",
                          ""displayTime"": 99.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Scroll Bar function that sets the maximum value of the"",
                          ""displayTime"": 103.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""scroll bar and also sets up appropriate values"",
                          ""displayTime"": 106.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""for the large and small change properties."",
                          ""displayTime"": 110.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'll code that whenever we set the peaks."",
                          ""displayTime"": 113.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And we'll also code it whenever the user resizes the control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 118.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""which we can detect by overriding the Un-resize method."",
                          ""displayTime"": 122.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We also need to make sure that when the user scrolls"",
                          ""displayTime"": 128.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the scroll bar, we redraw, so let's handle the"",
                          ""displayTime"": 131.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Scroll event of our scroll bar and code invalidate again"",
                          ""displayTime"": 135.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""if you remember this tells our control,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 143.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""it needs to repaint itself."",
                          ""displayTime"": 145.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Now in the Paint method of our control currently, we're"",
                          ""displayTime"": 149.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""completely ignoring where the horizontal scroll bar is set"",
                          ""displayTime"": 151.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to and just starting drawing the waveform from the beginning"",
                          ""displayTime"": 155.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""so let's say that the Start peak"",
                          ""displayTime"": 159.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""is the value of the horizontal scroll bar."",
                          ""displayTime"": 161.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""and now we keep drawing peaks until"",
                          ""displayTime"": 166.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""we either reach the right hand edge of the control"",
                          ""displayTime"": 168.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""or we reach the last peak but now that calculation"",
                          ""displayTime"": 171.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""needs to take into account what the Start peak is."",
                          ""displayTime"": 174.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""And when we actually get the peak that we're going"",
                          ""displayTime"": 179.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to draw again, we take into account Start peak."",
                          ""displayTime"": 180.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Don't worry too much if you found these calculations"",
                          ""displayTime"": 186.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""a little bit hard to follow but quite often this is typical"",
                          ""displayTime"": 188.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""of what you will be doing inside a Paint event handler."",
                          ""displayTime"": 191.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""You'll be making various calculations depending on the size"",
                          ""displayTime"": 195.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""that's available and working out what needs to be drawn"",
                          ""displayTime"": 198.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""where so now we should have working scroll bars."",
                          ""displayTime"": 201.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Let's run our application and see it in action."",
                          ""displayTime"": 205.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""We'll load up the podcast and now you can see"",
                          ""displayTime"": 211.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""the scroll bar shows, we can scroll quite a way"",
                          ""displayTime"": 215.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to the right so let's do that."",
                          ""displayTime"": 217.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""Thanks to double buffering this is quite a smooth"",
                          ""displayTime"": 221.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""scrolling experience and you can see we can scroll"",
                          ""displayTime"": 223.4409891
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""right to the right-hand edge of this podcast."",
                          ""displayTime"": 228.4409891
                        }
                      ]
                    },
