                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""this course have been fully implemented"",
                          ""displayTime"": 34.7231779
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""throughout the demo application."",
                          ""displayTime"": 37.7231779
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""This application has still got a little bit further"",
                          ""displayTime"": 39.7231779
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""to go before it's really done."",
                          ""displayTime"": 41.7231779
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I think it's also appropriate at this point, though,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 46.7231779
                        },
                        {
                          ""text"": ""I take a moment to thank the DotNet Podcasters,"",
                          ""displayTime"": 48.7231779
